.SS "int evutil_parse_sockaddr_port (const char *str, struct sockaddr *out, int *outlen)"

.PP
Parse an IPv4 or IPv6 address, with optional port, from a string\&. Recognized formats are:
.IP "\(bu" 2
[IPv6Address]:port
.IP "\(bu" 2
[IPv6Address]
